{"version": 2, "width": 120, "height": 30, "timestamp": 1774770239, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/zsh", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}, "title": "cuong-node asks phong-node a question"}
[0.0, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H\u001b[38;2;210;150;80m\u001b[1m\u2500\u2500 cuong-node  \u00b7  dev  \u00b7  project: alpha \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\u001b[38;2;210;150;80m$\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;140;130;115mAsk phong-node what they're currently working on.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.2, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[38;2;225;218;205mI'll check who's online and then send the question.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.8, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[38;2;80;200;200m\u001b[1m\u26a1 ccom_online_nodes\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\u251c \u001b[38;2;225;218;205m(no args)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.6, "o", "  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2502 [\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2502   \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m{\"nodeId\":\"f7a2..\",\"name\":\"phong-node\",\"vertical\":\"frontend\"},\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2502   \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m{\"nodeId\":\"c3b1..\",\"name\":\"blue-node\",\"vertical\":\"qa\"}\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2514 ]\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.2, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[38;2;225;218;205mphong-node is online. Sending the question now.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.8, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[38;2;80;200;200m\u001b[1m\u26a1 ccom_ask\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\u251c \u001b[38;2;225;218;205mquestion:    \"What are you working on right now?\"\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\u251c \u001b[38;2;225;218;205mtargetNode:  \"phong-node\"\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.6, "o", "  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2502 {\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2502   \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\"queryId\":    \"9e4f1a2b-c83d-4e5f-a1b2-d3e4f5a6b7c8\",\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2502   \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\"broadcast\":  false,\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2502   \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\"networkSent\": true\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;100;200;100m\u2514 }\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.2, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[38;2;225;218;205mMessage sent to phong-node (queryId: 9e4f1a2b).\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.6, "o", "  \u001b[38;2;225;218;205mWaiting for their reply \u2014 it will arrive as a channel event.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[7.5, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[38;2;255;140;60m\u001b[1m\u25c6 channel event\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;2;140;130;115msource=ccom  type=query_respond\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\u251c from:    \u001b[38;2;210;150;80mphong-node\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;2;140;130;115m\u2514 content: \u001b[38;2;225;218;205m\"Working on the new auth flow \u2014 just finished the token refresh logic.\"\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.2, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[38;2;225;218;205mphong-node replied: they're working on the auth flow,\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.5, "o", "  \u001b[38;2;225;218;205mspecifically the token refresh logic.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.2, "o", "\r\n"]
